he materials and the precision of the jeweller’s hand. Produced in a strictly limited and numbered edition of 1,785 pieces of 125 mL, each set is accompanied by a 30 mL travel spray and a funnel, allowingRouge Bonheur—an ode to happiness, luck, and joy—to be carried wherever life leads.",2026,"Ginger, Pepper","Rose, Magnolia","Cedar, White Musk",N/A,"fresh spicy, fresh, warm spicy, rose",Delphine Jelk,https://fimgs.net/mdimg/perfume-thumbs/375x500.122063.jpg,for women and men,N/A,N/A,2026-06-09 11:30:15,Fragrantica
