https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Guerlain/Imagine-Guerlain-by-Shourouk-Rhaiem-98370.html,Imagine Guerlain by Shourouk Rhaiem Guerlainfor women and men,Guerlain,4.28,71,"Imagine Guerlain by Shourouk RhaiembyGuerlainis a fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance.Imagine Guerlain by Shourouk Rhaiemwas launched in 2024. The nose behind this fragrance is Thierry Wasser. Top notes are Orange Blossom and Orange; middle note is Benzoin; base note is Sandalwood.Maison Guerlain presents an exclusive, limited-edition Christmas rendezvous: Imagine Guerlain, in collaboration with Shourouk Rhaiem, the renowned French jewelry designer. To celebrate the festive season with sparkle and magic, Shourouk Rhaiem unveils her dazzling, multi-colored world. For the 2024 vintage, the iconic Flacon aux Abeilles is adorned with a radiant jewel—a wearable cuff bracelet that can be worn on the wrist. This exceptional piece encases the Imagine Guerlain Eau de Parfum, an amber-colored nectar with floral and woody notes, perfect for adding a festive touch to the holiday season. This exclusive fragrance is available only on Guerlain.com and in select Guerlain boutiques.The Imagine Guerlain Eau de Parfum is an extraordinary creation designed to capture the magic of Christmas with grandeur. Luxurious and timeless, it opens with majestic floral notes, highlighted by a hint of zesty orange. As the fragrance develops, it reveals rich, vibrant woody notes, culminating in an intense, magical scent with a warm and sensual composition.For 170 years, the Flacon aux Abeilles has been a symbol of craftsmanship and artistry. Produced by the glassmaker Pochet du Courval, the bottle is decorated with intricate festoons and golden bees, meticulously enhanced with fine gold detailing. The signature cord, tied by hand by the skilled Dames de Table at the Guerlain Workshops, adds a final touch of elegance. This year, the shimmering jewel envisioned by Shourouk Rhaiem elevates the bottle's design, allowing wearers to take a piece of this exceptional creation with them.For the first time ever, the iconic Flacon aux Abeilles is adorned with a striking creation that doubles as a wearable accessory. The large cuff, encrusted with sparkling rhinestones, features an imaginary flower at its center, with Guerlain's double G emblem blooming from its heart. The petals of this enchanting flower shimmer in bluish hues, making the jewel an embodiment of festive magic and sparkle.Shourouk Rhaiem, a jewelry designer who began crafting her first crystal-covered pieces in her Parisian studio over fifteen years ago, draws inspiration from her Tunisian roots, the pop culture of the 1980s, and the glamour of Hollywood films. Her playful and poetic approach to design transforms ordinary objects into extraordinary creations, embellished with a myriad of crystals in various sizes and colors.This exclusive, limited-edition release consists of 3,310 numbered pieces. Each 125 mL bottle comes with a 30 mL spray and a funnel, allowing you to carry this exceptional fragrance with you wherever you go.",2024,"Orange Blossom, Orange",Benzoin,Sandalwood,N/A,"citrus, amber, white floral, warm spicy",Thierry Wasser,https://fimgs.net/mdimg/perfume-thumbs/375x500.98370.jpg,for women and men,N/A,N/A,2026-06-09 11:37:35,Fragrantica
